  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: I want to see my request/send messages to reflect the currency I selected in profile -> currency\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nCurrency is applied through all the places, so if I selected RUR - all my /send and /request messages are in RUR\r\n- send / request for ETH\r\n- send / request for tokens \r\n- collectibles (when supported)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n`/send` and `/request` messages are always shown in USD\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/41534670-fcf46062-7307-11e8-95aa-1074f73a2404.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Change currency to any except USD\r\n- Send some ETH in 1x1 chat\r\n- Request some ETH in 1x1 chat",
